

low_fuel 10.0 5.0

  Your Hovertank is low on fuel! 
  Fuel does regenerate slowly when you keep your fuel consumption down.
  Fuel will regenerate quicker if you land your tank.
  Either slow down for a while, or find the closest fuel pad and refuel there.  
  You can target your closest fuel pad with <target_closest_fuel>.
{end}



low_health 50.0 2.5

  Your Hovertank is heavily damaged!
  Health does regenerate slowly, but you probably want to repair at a base.
  Find the closest repair pad with <target_closest_repair>.
  Or land and your health will regenerate at a slightly higher than normal rate.	
{end}


cargo_pickup_fail 25.0 5.0

  You can only carry one thing at a time!
  You could ask somebody else to pick it up for you while you guard it.
{end}

uplink_pickup_fail_tournament 25.0 5.0

  Can't pickup enemy Uplink when game isn't in tournament mode.
{end}


non_base_cargo_close_and_not_carrying 15.0 5.0

  There is a cargo nearby!  Target it with <target_closest_cargo>.
  You can pick it up by touching it.
{end}


near_unpowered_units 20.0 5.0

  Hey look!  Neutral units.  
  You can take these over by deploying an energy unit into their vicinity.
{end}
